text: The 2015–16 Botola 2 was the 54th season of Botola 2, the second division of the Moroccan football league. The season was started on the 5 September 2015 and concluded the 15 May 2016. The season break was from 9 until 29 January 2016. == Team change == ===Teams relegated from 2014–15 Botola=== * Ittihad Khemisset * Chabab Atlas Khenifra ===Teams promoted from 2014–15 GNFA 1=== * Rachad Bernoussi * Olympique Marrakech == Table == Category:Botola seasons
